                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-1298" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH COLBY</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I took two hoys at first—I had only seen one in the shop, but they were both running together—I never lost sight of the prisoner—I am sure he was in the shop.</p>
